Jesus Christ.  That might be the most ham fisted character intro in history.  The Smallville & especially the Kevin Conroy stuff was terrible, but one good thing they did was mock and then erase the Birds of Prey TV show from history.

snippet.textDisplay: I can't stand hypocrisy. Most fans hated Ezra for no reason at all, he is a great actor, and now everyone loves him. I love Grant to death and have been watching The Flash since it started but for copyright and corporate bull crap reasons, Grant could not be the DCEU Flash. I liked Ezra and his idea of interpreting a darker Flash and not one being annoyed by Iris, is THE BEST IDEA ever for a solo movie. I hope this cameo means that the writers are finally on board with Ezra and they all can deliver a great Flash. Remember, WB is not Disney, thank God. Why do we want to ruin these comic shows like Disney ruined Marvel and Star Wars? It beats me.
